result.name: Sun Hing Congee

reviews.text: This little local restaurant was our best choice for our breakfast. Avalon congee was tasty.
Really good place for congee and hot pot rice. I recommend their soy stir fried noodles and hot pot rice (臘腸雞飯)
Great local place for congee. Prepared in front of you and the pig blood congee is especially recommend. The soya milk is also very good

A good local spot for congee. Good tasting baste and lots of ingredients for the congee. Although still adapting the old style of congee shops, it looks a little more modern. Food is tasty and price is good. Would come here again.
My go to place for Congee. Local, cheap, super tasty

result.name: 新興發粥店

reviews.text: 好吃😋
新興發粥店位於電器道，顧名思義是供應粥品、油條、炒麵等傳統食品，更有多種套餐組合供客人選擇，價格不高但出品也普通，不過不失。
啱我返工長時間。唔得閒在家煮。佢4餸飯好好。有菜。瓜。豆腐。魚。肉任配搭，煲仔。盅頭会反，佢叫多樣化粥店。開到12点
This little local restaurant was our best choice for our breakfast. Avalon congee was tasty.
食品有問題，豬肝苦、價格高、招乎自大。
